--Purpose--

    Importing Contacts from Google & updating Google Calender for a User

----[ Features
    
    Import contacts from Google into addressbook
    Update the calendar on Google.
    

----[ Installation

    Install just like any other plugin, just untar it in the plugin directory,
    it will create a directory called google_intg
    Run conf.pl and add the plugin to active list.

    Edit config.php to change the
      
    

